.env
.env.local
.env.production

# NOTE: server/uploads/ and server/data/db.json used to be gitignored so
# personal data wasn't accidentally committed on local dev. They're now
# tracked so that admin edits made on Render can be auto-persisted back to
# the repo (see server/lib/persist.js). If you want them ignored on your
# local dev, add them back to a personal .git/info/exclude instead.

